item.title: CVE-2018-1197|2024-09-16T18:49:32.654Z -- dell%20emc -- windows%20stemcells
item.description: In Windows Stemcells versions prior to 1200.14, apps running inside containers in Windows on Google Cloud Platform are able to access the metadata endpoint. A malicious developer could use this access to gain privileged credentials.
